data.description: Nestled amidst breathtaking scenery, this exquisite 4-bedroom, 3-bathroom residence commands attention with its panoramic million-dollar views that span the valley. Perched on nearly half an acre, this captivating property offers the perfect retreat for those seeking a lifestyle immersed in natural splendor. Upon entering, you're greeted by a grand open floor plan adorned with soaring vaulted ceilings and skylights that bathe the space in natural light. The expansive living room seamlessly transitions into the newly remodeled kitchen. Equipped with modern appliances and wired for both gas or electric range oven. Retreat to the luxurious master bedroom and immerse yourself in the breathtaking mountain and lake views. The generously sized walk-in closet provides ample storage, while the adjoining bathroom offers a spa-like ambiance. Step outside onto the expansive deck overlooking the captivating valley vista. The finished walk-out basement provides ample space for additional living and entertainment, featuring two additional bedrooms with newer carpet, a full bathroom, an oversized laundry area, and a cozy family room. While enveloped by serene surroundings, you'll find yourself just minutes from shops, restaurants, and the alluring Beckwith Reservoir, offering endless opportunities for recreation and outdoor exploration. This residence embodies the true essence of Colorado living, where breathtaking views and a harmonious connection to nature converge.
